<TITLE> President hosts X-mas reception </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Dec 25 (bdnews24.com)--President Zillur Rahman hosted a reception in honour of Christian community at Bangabhaban on Friday on the occasion of the Christmas. The president exchanged greetings with the guests and cut a Christmas cake. Archbishop Poulinus Costa, diplomats of different countries, leaders of the Christian community and people from different professions joined the programme. State minister for religious affairs Md Shahjahan Miah and state minister for cultural affairs Promod Mankin were also present at the reception
